data.title: The Bunker Restaurant & Bar
data.meta_description: Join us at our newly opened food truck and a 40 foot indoor/outdoor bar!
data.text:
TATER TOTS - 6

Everyone loves tater tots!

Served with Bunker Sauce

Rusty Allen keys (Fries) - 6

Skin-on fries served with our hosue made Bunker sauce.

SMOKED WINGS - 9

Fried wings crisped to perfection. Choose plain, tossed in BBQ, or gochujang sauce with a side of ranch or blue cheese.

TOTCHOS - 11

Tater tots topped with smoked pulled pork, black beans, cotija cheese, pickled onion, BBQ sauce, and house made ranch dressing.

CBR Totchos - 12

Tater tots topped with smoked chicken, applewood smoked bacon, and house made ranch dressing.

BLT - 10

Applewood smoked bacon, lettuce, tomato, baconjam, and rosemary aioli on a toasted bun. Add smoked chicken - $3

SMOKED CHICKEN SANDWICH - 12

Smoked chicken, melted Gouda cheese, house-made Bunker Sauce, kale slaw, bread and butter pickles.

Add: Bacon - 2

sPICY CHICKEN SANDWICH - 12

Fried spicy chicken breast, lettuce, tomato, onion, and pickles on a toasted bun.

Make it buffalo - $1

JALAPENO POPPER SMASH BURGER - 15

This is one poppin’ burger! Two 4 oz beef patties, cheddar, bacon, jalapeno cream cheese, pickled jalapenos, and garden pepper aioli on a toasted bun.

BACON AND BLEU SMASH BURGER - 15

Two 4 oz beef patties, bleu cheese crumbles, applewood smoked bacon, bacon onion jam, and onion ring on a toasted bun.

“THE OAKESY” BASIC SMASH BURGER - 12

It’s pretty basic! Two 4 oz beef patties with lettuce, tomato, and pickled onion on a toasted bun. Add Cheese $1 – cheddar, swiss, gouda, pepper jack Add Bacon - $2

WESTERN BURGER - 16

This burger is a beast! Two 4 oz beef patties, smoked pulled pork, applewood smoked bacon, melted gouda cheese, house made ranch, and BBQ sauce on a toasted bun.

MUSHROOM SWISS SMASH BURGER - 14

Two 4 oz beef patties, melted swiss cheese, balsamic marinated mushrooms, and rosemary aioli on a toasted bun.

bbq pULLED PORK sANDWICH - 12

House-smoked BBQ pulled pork topped with cheddar cheese, pickles, and spicy garden pepper aioli on a toasted bun.

Black Bean Burger - 12

Our vegetarian option. Black bean veggie burger with lettuce, tomatoe, and pickled onion on a toasted bun. Add cheese $1 - cheddar, gouda, pepper jack, swiss

The only bar at a paintball field on the East Coast! Featuring four rotating draft lines, 55 inch TVs playing your favorite paintball videos, and a collection of historical paintball gear on display. Take a seat at our 32 foot long live edge bar after your paintball session, enjoy some delicious food from our food truck, and chase it with an ice cold adult beverage.
